value.title: Trump: Kavanaugh should 'sue the women' who accused him during his Supreme Court confirmation
value.excerpt: President Trump on Monday said Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh should “sue the women” who leveled “false and disgusting accusations” against him during his confirmation process to the high court in 2018.

value.title: Jill Biden to campaign in Texas as Dems look to flip Lone Star State
